[2026-03-09T15:45:16Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UpaUTTXPZsazQJWq9qtD8R","type":"tool_result","content":"40:// WithLogBroadcaster sets the log broadcaster for SSE streaming.\n157:\th.mux.HandleFunc(\"GET /api/runs/{id}/stream\", h.handleAPIStream)\n713:// handleAPIStream serves an SSE stream of log lines for a run.\n716:func (h *Handler) handleAPIStream(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n765:\t\t\t\t// Stream finished (run completed)\n780:// streamFullLog reads the archived full.log file and sends its entries as SSE events.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01LbJUrEpKUsTxPgt13TBUr4","session_id":"e316c9bd-e648-4c15-80fc-32844599c155","uuid":"f64ae087-1de9-409b-8edf-87387e706d4b"}
